-- Arabtec Unit, Musawa Holding Form Construction Joint Venture in Bahrain
-- B y   S h a j i   M a t h e w
-- 2010-10-19T03:59:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-19/arabtec-unit-musawa-holding-form-construction-joint-venture-in-bahrain.html
Arabtec Holding Co., the biggest
builder in the United Arab Emirates by market value, said its
unit signed an agreement to form a joint venture in Bahrain.  Arabtec Construction LLC and Musawa Holding will jointly
execute construction projects under the newly established
company called Arabtec-Musawa WLL, the company said in a
statement to the Dubai bourse today.  “This step comes as part of the company’s strategy to
diversify geographically outside the United Arab Emirates,”
Arabtec Chief Executive Officer Riad Kamal said in the
statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Shaji Mathew at 
 shajimathew@bloomberg.net  